### U校园 API 调试文件
### 使用方法：
### 1. 安装 VS Code REST Client 插件
### 2. 填写下方的 @username 和 @password
### 3. 点击 "Send Request" 发送请求

@base_url = https://ucontent.unipus.cn
@sso_url = https://sso.unipus.cn
@uai_url = https://uai.unipus.cn

### 请填写你的账号信息
@username = 17716841865
@password = ff@00000

### 登录后会自动填充这些变量
@open_id = 
@service_ticket = 
@jwt_token = 
@course_id = course-v2:75bd6c9770028fd+ljddzg_rw+20230403


# ==================== SSO 登录 ====================

### 1. SSO 登录（获取 serviceTicket 和 openId）
# @name sso_login
POST {{sso_url}}/sso/0.1/sso/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest

{
  "service": "https://u.unipus.cn/user/comm/login?school_id=",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "captcha": "",
  "rememberMe": "on",
  "captchaCode": "",
  "encodeCaptha": ""
}

### 2. 获取验证码（当返回 1502 时调用）
# @name get_captcha
POST {{sso_url}}/sso/4.0/sso/image_captcha2


# ==================== UAI 平台 ====================

### 3. UAI - 获取课程列表
# @name uai_course_list
GET {{uai_url}}/learn/api/v2/course/list
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 4. UAI - 提交课程进度
# @name uai_submit_progress
POST {{uai_url}}/learn/api/v2/record/progress
Content-Type: application/json
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

{
  "courseId": "{{course_id}}",
  "unitId": "unit_001",
  "openId": "{{open_id}}",
  "duration": 30
}


# ==================== UContent 平台 ====================

### 5. UContent - 获取课程详情
# @name ucontent_course_details
GET {{base_url}}/course/api/v4/lms/course/details?courseId={{course_id}}
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 6. UContent - 获取课程内容（加密）
# @name ucontent_content
GET {{base_url}}/course/api/v3/content/{{course_id}}/64f1f5410001019/default
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 7. UContent - 获取答案与解析
# @name ucontent_answer
GET {{base_url}}/course/api/v3/answer/{{course_id}}/64f1f5410001019/default
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 8. UContent - 保存进度（text/video 类型）
# @name ucontent_save_progress
POST {{base_url}}/api/mobile/user_group/{{course_id}}/64f1f5410001019/progress
Content-Type: application/json
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

{
  "groupId": "64f1f5410001019",
  "status": 2,
  "version": "default"
}

### 9. UContent - 提交答案（task 类型）
# @name ucontent_submit_task
POST {{base_url}}/course/api/v3/newExploration/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

{
  "quesDatas": [
    {
      "instanceId": "ques_001",
      "answer": "{}",
      "context": "{}",
      "contextVersion": 0,
      "answerVersion": 0
    }
  ],
  "groupId": "657ebd3c0000d13",
  "isCompleted": [true],
  "thirdPartyJudges": "[]",
  "submitType": 1,
  "hideLoading": true,
  "associationGroupId": "",
  "associationUnitId": "",
  "courseId": "{{course_id}}",
  "openId": "{{open_id}}",
  "version": "default"
}

### 10. UContent - 查询课程进度
# @name ucontent_course_progress
GET {{base_url}}/course/api/v2/course_progress/{{course_id}}/{{open_id}}/default
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 11. UContent - 查询单元进度
# @name ucontent_unit_progress
GET {{base_url}}/course/api/v2/course_progress/{{course_id}}/64f1e6350000caa/{{open_id}}/default
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 12. UContent - 查询 Group 状态
# @name ucontent_group_state
GET {{base_url}}/api/mobile/user_module/{{course_id}}/64f1f5410001019/progress/v2
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}

### 13. UContent - 查询用户答案
# @name ucontent_user_answer
GET {{base_url}}/api/mobile/user_module/{{course_id}}/64f1f5410001019-default
X-Annotator-Auth-Token: {{jwt_token}}
